o_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTgpV6iLwUw-UwuelT_o8ZpJLQhTjc3ZX54U8ugiMyQsE4RQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"5 個月前\",\"text\":\"內用空間很小，不論室內室外座位都排得很擠\\n也因為新竹風超級大，很不推薦坐外面\\n當室內用餐的人離開之後，老闆會先詢問已經在室外用餐的顧客要不要換位子\\n所以不要一來看到裡面有位子就開心的衝進去囉\\n\\n雖然座位小小的\\n但是餐點好吃也是真的\\n\\\"簡單吃\\\"的內容簡單也很美味\\n有火腿、培根、沙拉、炒蛋、軟法跟馬鈴薯薯條\\n個人吃完感覺8分飽，配上附餐紅茶剛剛好\\n\\n整體來說，個人覺得空間及環境不是適合悠閒聊天，長時間待著的早午餐店，是比較適合一個人來享用的早午餐\",\"time\":1735008236,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"吳小台\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102526694259261132681/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHa6G-M5eOShjxITUtgnjGDDP3dcfoZSK2gZ52hX6mcAdzgwNp=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 個月前\",\"text\":\"店面位置不起眼，但餐點非常好吃，位子雖不多，可不熄滅想吃美食的熱情\\n\\n吃飽飽套餐、泰式卡拉雞腿三明治，好吃！\",\"time\":1736565058,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNQYfv8xjFTeEh68FIrwESh_5VuX1AWs467czpAUWH0XKjil3jMt8WCBFpr0BHpmRQK1svW6twQpMj42e_MRXgB8NsKIot4YUY5oOIg_bl--K1LVrogLGKaEbV9292Lbt2k52U9eSacAAlh0pLrJRSMkDyM2YzivK0Svu_2qro9yUr5p8OLcgF_bhwqylxsPzBxD_HcvNOB1nQgtO1Frps-U8ROn2rpCqE99jaseyFjrLaax69kCwXQpy4wGO4kqRhGzZsnNMcFYj33PEsOXSs7QiSjCkEWBvjycJCUCs1enlBzAgMbq3j-gn_N0I2qRpabZbz3zWW3blXm1chpcRPr0_TfIgdeLOpejBaupi1vJtUSA_VGVCo4PWZvvozGul0Zg2S9xcXdYwXPRdZe5QyEspjsfCFPl53AGHrdhqDbN6gKReJEEK0PU08d42-ScQLmzjGk_kbXIKqBoyF1jrgICmDqK4EAC1iNpDsRhbYVQloaYn4v-nupWFZqCqUyisLgZ8xd6ukxJySRE8u07E7gNuEJo4Z72m8jR17tlQZv8Yfn4jroUI1QlMxojACwTt8XTI8SQvBZMHslkPlICkdZ3okUvz9GKYZL41VWZr3A1v0i_3bo4O2-5e4rrnP9tNXKZ6Q\",\"AXQCQNTJNNvpIzolgOeCRcmAtuzL2dcfD22ddtcvfJKNzA8IjDa2IZF94S1v8-UNwUOstU0RmuG98pO45ISk9iGse5PVEjJNL1Aq2KJS8i7t04DnVsVN27yUWYXaX2n_8l7dl83R-x0APBamDk5XjK39M6YJRcDQQ7hDwZ_7MruvcIeyHPhLx1GGwPQg5RvSxQqCSWV39N58GrOdfIQuXeta8dm5loCu-7szy5Xbpv5_wEINmaKfr_-XB53blg0ScnTJ3lynLVRdDvBUHN2vtn1N0mgo-r6ryEx2rtpy-utnU9rhs_DFcpRkwpKeGR-V3LytTUqeno4eQMVSMNpkrQBNpllBmRKS3LRgCk6sNdP3iakzryfmOCVy1xQaRwfI3