t.com/a/ACg8ocLZ0N_hGmvJl863WYKqXcMmqRZHyzEumYedlzC-WAd6Eyom9A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"9 個月前\",\"text\":\"剛出社會曾來過一兩次，之後好久沒再來過。覺得是個學生或初出茅廬打牙祭的好地方。很colorful 的名稱與裝潢，快20年了，與記憶相比有點老舊了。\\n但焗烤依然很懷念，很多選擇，主食還可以麵，飯或芋泥三選二的搭配。義大利麵是通心粉不是麵條。整個口感及肉質很順，沒有太鹹或是花草香料來混淆。\\n紅茶有幾種選擇。我選了羅漢果紅茶... 完全沒感受到紅茶而是羅漢果味道佔據。不會太甜，還不錯。\",\"time\":1725803492,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"劉陳怡君\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102919309769263917840/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJS8Axby4hQUlZzD1sbWU1QO5nbWQTg-orsOhQnrLftzZ-f1w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 年前\",\"text\":\"高中畢業後常和同學來，是愛店之一～\\n\\n在當年很少餐廳會有一半洋芋一半麵（或飯）的選項，即使是20多年後的現在也依舊不多。\\n洋芋豪好吃～\\n今天吃焗烤羅勒牛，醬汁都有巴在麵上，非常入味😋😋😋\\n起司和當年一樣給得很大氣，讚👍👍\\n\\n今天是滿滿回憶的一餐，跟記憶中一樣好吃😋\",\"time\":1699108236,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Liz Tien\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109285781874994716490/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpZrxbD_rsQd42CVJhimFXKv-L6fm6Wg1PKpKO77TXxBSbzWk2Og=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"焗烤洋芋系列\\n非常好吃美味\\n店內用餐環境\\n非常寬敞舒適\\n老闆親切有禮\\n每次都會想一來再來👍👍👍👍👍\",\"time\":1746180162,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNSeRv3nXVY29QK3xuPeFLgCj0agjAtcW5D6KeV7p_-zVEGiO_hn_dCQ-Hd2fLgn3PCeNAI0okFAu9N8Kv2v1rAa_5P-FWRcET-E1ozKWeO7UC_i7pNo7zY1_PWwVAtDx_VG5hhWvO0UaM8tBAPeEpWl_T6WN_V5dpsExC4Rd9m601AOxXlHe3NJgmzyTAMIbQrXPMHu2-yh0ekRbi_9kVUov3bubWhPanBadoNm6TVaTVYyAwZ6wbKUMZ1NLA2AtNreEYIY02CsWvKrlf3VqEttLIl9B1-7Lpz_pu3voksOfkTXWmBdipixnURPUkYXt2ulHEnFO8Y\",\"AXQCQNTIRFszAsE8N0GoLBC36-XRbYcBm0CRe4kHJJ1ld17mfscIOveBfJZYl80ONYYoP_hi8OTu4yO1pmicXQEgXHMPAcVl4N_MTheI7mLPXjSR1JwHwzlh4aqL5zG1CqLPHCqFH5HdGjclbz1nSpidSHwQtgL2lX1dviMcQ-0fLbewDEwfoJX5QGA4LRUXb5_uDZcai2A5471KJyNpdu0CTnTuLxvOgPMhS-vIr20tqdKeVHMxVXtNN